<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa5">
<l>māyaṉai maṉṉu vaṭa maturai maintaṉait</l>
<l>tūya peru nīr yamuṉait tuṟaivaṉai</l>
<l>āyar kulattiṉil tōṉṟum aṇi viḷakkait</l>
<l>tāyaik kuṭal viḷakkam ceyta tāmōtaraṉait</l>
<l>tūyōmāy vantu nām tūmalar tūvit toḻutu</l>
<l>vāyiṉāl pāṭi maṉattiṉāl cintikkap</l>
<l>pōya piḻaiyum pukutaruvāṉ niṉṟaṉavum</l>
<l>tīyiṉil tūcākum ceppēlōr empāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As we come purified,</l>
<l>worshipping by bestrewing pure flowers,</l>
<l>singing thanks to [our] mouths [and] thinking thanks to [our] minds</l>
<l rend="indent">of the Black One,</l>
<l rend="indent">the young Man from northern Mathurā, where He remains [forever],</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who resides on the banks of the pure Yamunā of abundant waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">the beautiful Light that appeared in the cowherd caste,</l>
<l rend="indent">Dāmodara who enlightened [His] mother’s womb,</l>
<l>[our] past sins and the ones that wait to approach [us]</l>
<l>will become [like] cotton [caught] in fire.</l>
<l>Say [it],</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
